          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The K5 Blazer was Chevrolet's answer to the Ford Bronco. It was quite successful, too, and the boxy K5 Blazer of 1973-1991 is one of the most beloved classic 4x4s of all time. It's right up there with the original Jeep CJ series.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
