        "caption": "Image Via Restore a Muscle Car"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "However, we're big fans of the original 1969-1972 style, which shared its styling with the popular \"Action Line\" pickups of the same era. We found this 1972 example right here on Motorious, at ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Restore a Muscle Car",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
